Gabriel and Legion were my favorite, but all three are really good films that have I feel a high degree of truth to them. Legion is wonderful because it shows the love that the Angels have for us and warns that Angels commanded by the Heavenly Father can demolish rebelious children if we go beyond the point of no return. Gabriel is amazing because it shows how we come to this plane with a powerful sense of purpose but we forget about it, get discouraged or become compromised if we don't hold tightly on the Alliance with our Creator. Highly recommended to everyone no matter your background.

Actually, this trifecta is a good deal.  Scott Stewart is a filmaker to watch.  I loved both LEGION & PRIEST while Gabriel was just simply boring.  If you have 10$ or less...go for it.  3 films at that price are a bargain.  Enjoy, 4 stars is a good n fair rating.
